select interface, 5GRJ and ((chain H and resi 27+28+31+33+52+53+54+57+59+101+102+103+104+105+106) or (chain L and resi 32+34+93+97+99+95) or (chain A and resi 54+60+61+62+63+66+56+58+59+69+73+75+113+121+123+125+115+117+78))
